snippet.title: I'm Not Gay (ft. Amber Doig-Thorne & GiniCanBreathe)
snippet.description:
I'm just a metrosexual.

About InadequateChris:
On this channel you'll see "Socially Inadequate", a video blog series in which I talk about my experiences with social awkwardness and what I learned from them. I've talked about how to hide your emotions, how to stop blushing, how to make conversation and how to make eye contact.
You'll also see comedy sketches about movies, friends and idiots.
